'''羅興亞難民營大火'''始於2021年3月22日晚上，導致大面積的[[巴魯卡里難民營|巴魯卡里難民營]]被摧毀。大火導致至少15人死亡，400人失蹤，45,000人流離失所。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582201-20210324.htm |title=孟加拉羅興亞難民營大火至少15人死 |publisher=香港電台 |date=2021-03-24 |access-date=2021-03-24 |archive-date=2021-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326085007/https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582201-20210324.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==背景==
[[File:Rohingya_shacks_in_Balukhali.jpg|alt2=巴魯卡里內為罗兴亚难民興建的棚屋（2018年）]]
2017年，數十萬羅興亞穆斯林[[2017年羅興亞難民危機|離開緬甸若開邦]]，[[2016年羅興亞人危機|躲避政府的军事行動]]，估計共有超過100萬的羅興亞人流亡到其他國家，大部分人逃往[[孟加拉國|孟加拉國]]。根據聯合國的報告，{{as of|2019|07}}，有超過74萬羅興亞人從若開邦逃離或被趕出，到孟加拉國尋求庇護。<ref name="Al-Jazeera-Action3">{{cite web|date=2018-02-12|title=Myanmar: Security forces face 'action' over killings|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2018/02/myanmar-security-forces-face-action-killings-180211192034354.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180212103515/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2018/02/myanmar-security-forces-face-action-killings-180211192034354.html|archive-date=2018-02-12|access-date=2018-02-12|work=Al Jazeera News|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Refugees|first=United Nations High Commissioner for|title=Rohingya emergency|url=https://www.unhcr.org/rohingya-emergency.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301143615/https://www.unhcr.org/rohingya-emergency.html|archive-date=2021-03-01|access-date=2021-03-24|website=UNHCR|language=en}}</ref>[[巴魯卡里難民營|巴魯卡里難民營]]被認為是全球最大的難民營之一，居住了孟加拉100萬羅興亞人的十分之一，<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":2">{{Cite news|date=2021-03-23|title=Rohingya refugee camp fire: Several dead, hundreds missing and thousands homeless|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-56493708|access-date=2021-03-23|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325110407/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-56493708|dead-url=no}}</ref>覆蓋了{{convert|8000|acres|ha}}內34個營，<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|last=Bazar|first=Agence France-Presse in Cox's|date=2021-03-23|title=Bangladesh: 'massive' fire in Rohingya refugee camps forces 50,000 to flee|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/mar/22/bangladesh-fire-rohingya-refugee-camps|access-date=2021-03-23|website=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325082619/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/mar/22/bangladesh-fire-rohingya-refugee-camps|dead-url=no}}</ref>根據聯合國代表，超過一半的居民為兒童。<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|title=Massive Fire in Cox’s Bazar Damages Rohingya Refugee Camp|publisher=Voice of America - English|url=https://www.voanews.com/south-central-asia/massive-fire-coxs-bazar-damages-rohingya-refugee-camp|access-date=2021-03-24|website=www.voanews.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325191114/https://www.voanews.com/south-central-asia/massive-fire-coxs-bazar-damages-rohingya-refugee-camp|dead-url=no}}</ref>該地區曾在2017年發生過一次大火，令氣瓶爆炸。較小的火災亦在這次大火前兩天發生過，令一定數量的棚屋摧毀，2021年1月的火災亦燒毀了四間學校。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Bangladesh probes deadly fire at Rohingya camp, 400 missing|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/3/23/bangladesh-probes-deadly-fire-at-rohingya-refugee-camp|access-date=2021-03-23|website=www.aljazeera.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324165118/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/3/23/bangladesh-probes-deadly-fire-at-rohingya-refugee-camp|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==火災==
{{external media
   | image1 = [https://web.archive.org/web/20210325002428im_/https://im-media.voltron.voanews.com/Drupal/01live-166/styles/sourced/s3/2021-03/reuters_bangladesh_rohingya_camp_23Mar21.JPG 火災後的情況（攝於{{dts|2021.03.23}}）]{{r|:3}}
}}
2021年3月22日晚，位於[[科克斯巴扎爾|科克斯巴扎爾]]西南方的[[巴魯卡里難民營|巴魯卡里難民營]]突然出現火災，居民形容火勢從南邊開始迅速蔓延。根據[[聯合國難民署|聯合國難民署]]代表在3月23日所說，至少15人在大火中死亡，並有 400 人失蹤，560人受傷，45,000人流離失所，形容大火為「巨大且具毀滅性」，<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%BE%85%E8%88%88%E4%BA%9E%E4%BA%BA%E5%AD%9F%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%89%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91%E7%87%9F%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB%E9%87%80-15-%E6%AD%BB-%E6%95%B8%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%B5%81%E9%9B%A2%E5%A4%B1%E6%89%80-%E5%A6%82%E9%87%8D%E6%AD%B7-17-%E5%B9%B4%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E7%81%BD%E9%9B%A3/ |title=羅興亞人孟加拉難民營大火釀 15 死　數萬人流離失所　「如重歷 17 年緬甸災難」 |publisher=立場新聞 |date=2021-03-23 |access-date=2021-03-24 |archive-date=2021-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324131617/https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%BE%85%E8%88%88%E4%BA%9E%E4%BA%BA%E5%AD%9F%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%89%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91%E7%87%9F%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB%E9%87%80-15-%E6%AD%BB-%E6%95%B8%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%B5%81%E9%9B%A2%E5%A4%B1%E6%89%80-%E5%A6%82%E9%87%8D%E6%AD%B7-17-%E5%B9%B4%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E7%81%BD%E9%9B%A3/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[世界糧食計劃署|世界糧食計劃署]]指大火摧毀了部分食品配送倉庫，<ref name=":2" />診所、清真寺、社區中心等建築亦被摧毀。<ref name=":5" /> 

難民營內大部分的居民為女性和兒童<ref name=":3" />，而政府發言人指死亡人數中有一定數量為兒童，<ref name=":5">{{Cite web|title=Hundreds Missing In Aftermath Of Fire At Rohingya Refugee Camp|url=https://www.npr.org/2021/03/23/980393127/hundreds-missing-in-aftermath-of-fire-at-rohingya-refugee-camp|access-date=2021-03-24|website=NPR.org|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325021531/https://www.npr.org/2021/03/23/980393127/hundreds-missing-in-aftermath-of-fire-at-rohingya-refugee-camp|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，另有被困於瓦礫中的失蹤人口。[[国际红十字与红新月运动|国际红十字与红新月运动]]孟加拉代表團團長桑耶夫·卡夫利（{{lang|en|Sanjeev Kafley}}）指超過17,000間房屋被摧毀，數萬人流離失所。<ref name=":0" />這些房屋大部分使用[[竹|竹]]和[[苫布|苫布]]臨時地建成<ref name="france24-20210322">{{Cite web|date=2021-03-22|title=Deadly fire at Bangladesh refugee camp leaves tens of thousands of Rohingya homeless|url=https://www.france24.com/en/asia-pacific/20210322-massive-fire-forces-thousands-to-flee-rohingya-migrant-camps-in-bangladesh|access-date=2021-03-24|website=France 24|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325094808/https://www.france24.com/en/asia-pacific/20210322-massive-fire-forces-thousands-to-flee-rohingya-migrant-camps-in-bangladesh|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":5" />當地傳媒報告指在火災開始後8小時，火勢仍然在蔓延，<ref name=":1" />並持續至晚上。<ref name=":6" />一名羅興亞難民向[[全国公共广播电台|全国公共广播电台]]指「所有東西都消失了，數千個家庭無家可歸。」而{{tsl|en|Catholic Relief Services|天主教救濟服務}}指火災在下午爆發是不幸中的大幸，稱「人們當時正在移動，小朋友正在街上玩，令他們可以及時逃離現場」。<ref name=":5" />《[[印度时报|印度时报]]》指「至少4隊消防員竭力控制大火」，[[社会化媒体|-{zh-hans:社会媒体; zh-cn:社交媒体; zh-tw:社群媒體; zh-hk:社交媒體;}-]]片段顯示大量黑煙籠罩著整個營地。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Fire in Rohingya Camp: Fire guts hundreds of shelters in Rohingya refugee camp|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/fire-guts-hundreds-of-shelters-in-rohingya-refugee-camp/articleshow/81635857.cms|date=2021-03-22|access-date=2021-03-24|website=The Times of India|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323191118/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/fire-guts-hundreds-of-shelters-in-rohingya-refugee-camp/articleshow/81635857.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==反應==
火災發生的原因有待{{tsl|en|Bangladesh Police|孟加拉國警察}}調查。[[人權|人權]]監察者批評當局在難民營的四周放置[[有刺铁丝网|有刺铁丝网]]，指其妨礙了人們逃離火災現場，並可能導致死亡人數上升。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" />{{link-en|挪威難民理事會|Norwegian Refugee Council}}的[[揚·埃格蘭|揚·埃格蘭]]認為「營地如果沒有架設鐵絲網，這場悲劇可能就沒有那麼摧毀性。難民理事會工作人員曾聽過有難民指曾為了救家人、逃離火場、維持生命而穿越鐵絲網。」<ref name=":6" />然而，警方否認有關鐵絲網的指控，<ref name="france24-20210322" />，政府發言人指，「圍欄並非主要問題所在」，把問題歸咎於火勢蔓延的速度而非設施。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Aid workers struggle to reunite Rohingya children separated by deadly fire|url=https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asia/rohingya-camp-bangladesh-deadly-fire-children-separated-homeless-14479066|access-date=2021-03-24|website=CNA|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325191154/https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asia/rohingya-camp-bangladesh-deadly-fire-children-separated-homeless-14479066|dead-url=no}}</ref>

另一個質疑是為何火災看似在一個相對頻率出現，因為有當地消防員指在4天內已有3次火災，[[國際特赦組織|國際特赦組織]]指，這些觀點認為「火災發生頻率巧合，特別是前幾次火災的調查都沒有查出原因並重覆發生」，一名代表難民的發言人指「這些火災不斷發生的原因不明確」。<ref name=":0" />[[CBS_(電視網)|CBS]]報道指孟加拉當局懷疑有人[[縱火|縱火]]，稱「在短時間內發生這麼多火災不可能只巧合的事情」。<ref>{{Cite web|title=At least 15 killed by huge fire at Rohingya refugee camp in Cox's Bazar, Bangladesh|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/rohingya-refugee-camp-fire-bangladesh-coxs-bazar-myanmar-deaths-missing/|access-date=2021-03-24|website=www.cbsnews.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325041034/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/rohingya-refugee-camp-fire-bangladesh-coxs-bazar-myanmar-deaths-missing/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[世界糧食計劃署|世界糧食計劃署]]估計最終多達87,500人會受到火災影響，[[国际红十字与红新月运动|国际红十字与红新月运动]]更將這個數字估算至123,000人。由於[[熱帶氣旋|熱帶氣旋]]季即將迫近，援助機構指火災會持續嚴峻的狀態。<ref name=":6">{{Cite web|title=15 Dead, 560 Injured, After Rohingya Refugee Camp Fire|url=https://time.com/5949469/rohingya-refugee-camp-fire-bangladesh/|access-date=2021-03-24|website=Time|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325075841/https://time.com/5949469/rohingya-refugee-camp-fire-bangladesh/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

